### Updating Documents

Both `save_document` and `update_document` support `content_file` — an absolute file path to read content from instead of passing it inline. If both `content` and `content_file` are provided, `content_file` wins.

```javascript
// Update a document from a file you've already written
update_document({
  document_id: "doc-auth-plan",
  content_file: "/tmp/doc-auth-plan-v2.md"
})

// Or inline for small changes
update_document({
  document_id: "doc-auth-plan",
  title: "Auth System - Updated Plan",
  content: "# Updated content..."
})
```

